{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[0, 4]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"symbolPlacement","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"